==Twin towns – sister cities==

Buzău is twinned with:
* Oudenaarde, Belgium, since 1999
* Agios Dimitrios, Greece, since 2006
* Soroca, Moldova, since 2012
* Ialoveni, Moldova, since 2022
* Strășeni, Moldova, since 2022

